====== H8071: שִׂמְלָה (simlâh) ======

===== Source =====

perhaps by permutation for the feminine of  H5566  (through the idea of a   assuming the shape of the object beneath);

===== Meaning =====

cover a  dress , especially a  mantle

===== Definitions =====

  - cover
  - dress
  - mantle

===== Usage =====

apparel, cloth(-es, -ing), garment, raiment. Compare 
